{"tid":259234,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"裝修佬一定係最撚有腦既！","createTime":"2017-05-26T17:23:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-28T09:18:18.000Z","uid":7049,"like":7,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b5fb9da2054f229edfd2e9f9e8b2ce087c0ab53e","tid":259234,"uid":7049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T17:23:23.000Z","msg":"話說小弟屋企係3月既時候想裝修個廚房，<br />\n咁隔離屋就介紹左個師傅比我地<br />\n佢話佢個人都幾老實同做d野幾好...<br />\n咁就諗住搵佢做啦<br />\n起初做野都幾快手 又幫我地執返上手師傅d蘇州屎<br />\n我地屋企人都覺得 都ok咁<br />\n全拆再整返d底個d野 再鋪返磚都大約整左2星期<br />\n而個師傅都話大概個半月最遲都會整好晒<br />\n點知...整好晒所有磚個d野開始停工度呎整廚櫃個d<br />\n見佢停左成3星期咁 應該都訂左櫃啦<br />\n最後先同我地講未訂<br />\n都算撚數 依d唔係重點...<br />\n<br />\n我地整廚房仲諗住換埋道大門<br />\n咁就去揀好款再搵個師傅去訂啦（個裝修張約有包大門木門）<br />\n送到黎...就黎料喇...<br />\n都唔撚知個師傅點撚度野 <br />\n道門足足大左兩吋...<br />\n又要拎返廠整...<br />\n係拎返廠整期間 廚房要準備落黎啦<br />\n點知...老母whatsapp我...<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/27/011726_bbdf14737c251ef7d2e49c85f98c1100.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F27%2F011726_bbdf14737c251ef7d2e49c85f98c1100.jpg&h=dece85d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n吓？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但經過上次連門都度錯我已經睇化左<br />\n得啖笑<br />\n點知今日終於送道門落黎喇！！！<br />\n見遲遲10點幾都冇新圖睇<br />\n作為孝順仔緊係要食下花生啦<br />\n點知...<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/27/012035_e33c47c7d7ab8a63945bf507d4dc0960.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F27%2F012035_e33c47c7d7ab8a63945bf507d4dc0960.jpg&h=f5e8ff91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我想問邊家人間屋會係梯形門？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我想知我幾時可以返去住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n已經就快三個月 乜整個爛鬼廚房要成3個月既咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我屌 有冇人教我點屌個裝修佬 仲有萬零蚊尾數未比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8233c967e14014e457d3feab868b624321e419d","tid":259234,"uid":45301,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T17:26:56.000Z","msg":"咁撚樣都要問你不如死撚左佢"},{"pid":"3e1ae71acfe6bdb460cbea62656db7af46d6479c","tid":259234,"uid":7049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T17:30:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁撚樣都要問你不如死撚左佢</blockquote><br />\n全屋人都以為我唔講粗口<br />\n我用咁流利既粗口屌個師傅 我以後點算好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有個老細斯斯文文咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03630b55df6b350207e5404eceaba1573dc2d1b9","tid":259234,"uid":815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T17:32:08.000Z","msg":"鬧人一定要講粗口架咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"312ee9a21371de7bd49050d3691f7326c7148b0e","tid":259234,"uid":7049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T17:33:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鬧人一定要講粗口架咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最慘我堂阿哥話幫我 老母話多一事不如少一事<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38cc4fb0c05cef9541174647028bb86af5265d9c","tid":259234,"uid":57797,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T17:35:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>鬧人一定要講粗口架咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最慘我堂阿哥話幫我 老母話多一事不如少一事<br />\n<img src=\"/ass