islike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T17:43:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>鬧人一定要講粗口架咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最慘我堂阿哥話幫我 老母話多一事不如少一事<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好快你全屋都要裝修過，敢屌鳩裝修佬</blockquote><br />\n個裝修佬係隔離屋介紹 以為耶撚會好d 點知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實第一次可能佢錯（機會極微）<br />\n<br />\n第二次 100%大陸出錯<br />\n<br />\n如果你工作上有同大陸合作， 你覺得弱智既問題<br />\n<br />\n佢地都會經常出現</blockquote><br />\n正常弱智都知道門係直唔係上窄下闊 死啦 佢地冇腦可以有幾冇腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"006fa63ffbea81c5c36781c8f265530445eb7e87","tid":259234,"uid":13165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T17:43:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之後就會話扣關乜乜柒柒，裝修佬最興</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n扣關係藉口。大陸工廠甩期係事實<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"710bdde2e45c45f5bbd77e18a5904de1786af3f2","tid":259234,"uid":13165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T17:44:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>鬧人一定要講粗口架咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最慘我堂阿哥話幫我 老母話多一事不如少一事<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好快你全屋都要裝修過，敢屌鳩裝修佬</blockquote><br />\n個裝修佬係隔離屋介紹 以為耶撚會好d 點知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實第一次可能佢錯（機會極微）<br />\n<br />\n第二次 100%大陸出錯<br />\n<br />\n如果你工作上有同大陸合作， 你覺得弱智既問題<br />\n<br />\n佢地都會經常出現</blockquote><br />\n正常弱智都知道門係直唔係上窄下闊 死啦 佢地冇腦可以有幾冇腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思落手做個批<br />\n真係你唔好預佢有腦<br />\n佢地做到麻木曬"},{"pid":"2148674e9d8cbaab3177c52efd4e9923828f74c3","tid":259234,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T17:45:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6b0977bea1a139f16da58e84997322ffc6cc29cb","tid":259234,"uid":7049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T17:46:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>話你知搵裝修一定係搵新一代。老果d d牌係點來行內人都知。</blockquote><br />\nmore<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46d641a36a9d6f406aaf8817ec12f995aa310552","tid":259234,"uid":9586,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T17:58:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>話你知搵裝修一定係搵新一代。老果d d牌係點來行內人都知。</blockquote><br />\nmore<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n介紹10個有9個係伏，你諗下你介紹筆幾十萬生意佢做，介紹人中間無任何利益？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0301373a8fa6f712836b459145dc423a4aac9a3a","tid":259234,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T18:13:21.000Z","msg":"班友就係知你地怕麻煩,食撚住你"},{"pid":"f6b5bd98ca6d30dc6309e62dccdab5dc528a78eb","tid":259234,"uid":25212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T20:18:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>話你知搵裝修一定係搵新一代。老果d d牌係點來行內人都知。</blockquote><br />\nmore<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n老果代人際多..新個代岩岩起步..邊有機會發圍..有都比老果代圍喂喂自己攬晒嚕<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲有..客都會搵有經驗既老師傅做..<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解我咁清楚？因為我就係新一代想創業既裝修佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f008d4fb5db71799b9a579e5ee925e02babbf775","tid":259234,"uid":25212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T20:21:40.000Z","msg":"尾數係咪3成？扣反佢話佢交期唔準..你地要額外去租屋住..同埋你一日唔收貨佢都無尾數收既..你大不了同佢拖下時間既姐"},{"pid":"d6b65de22ea264a9a251e38658911206dbdf57f2","tid":259234,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T20:57:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>尾數係咪3成？扣反佢話佢交期唔準..你地要額外去租屋住..同埋你一日唔收貨佢都無尾數收既..你大不了同佢拖下時間既姐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nAgger 最多打官司<br />\n不過樓主咁怕事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"205771afaec8324ba1ee24a6d4eeb020088e239c","tid":259234,"uid":91636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T21:16:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>尾數係咪3成？扣反佢話佢交期唔準..你地要額外去租屋住..同埋你一日唔收貨佢都無尾數收既..你大不了同佢拖下時間既姐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nAgger 最多打官司<br />\n不過樓主咁怕事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最白痴既做法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你扣佢3成冇用，佢已經打個和<br />\n大多數裝修都冇簽合約<br />\n簽親約就唔會係原本個價<br />\n唔知唔好亂咁講，等陣佢走埋再搵人接手做<br />\n下手一定開個高價，廢是奶野<br />\n除非係原本識既<br />\n度錯門可以係睇錯尺，冇檢查多次<br />\n上窄下闊就一定係廠出錯<br />\n大陸廠做野唔睇到實1實就會咁樣<br />\n一批櫃可以錯一半都見過<br />\n全部櫃門重做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即場改櫃尺寸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39df9b29d47dea83edb3c998962b60a061d48689","tid":259234,"u